Program: Discovery
Title: Impossible Visions - inside the human brain
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry8y
Last Broadcast Date: 26 November 2002
The technology that makes the study of the unseen possible. Scientists believe they are close to being able to study the living brain as we think. This series examines the technology that makes all this possible. Presenter: Martin Redfern.